 of the Pharisees and Sadducees come to his baptism, he said unto them, O generation of vipers, who hath warned you to flee from the wrath to come?","year":26},{"id":"reccqYoDVRcdXtFzo","ref":"Matt.3.8","text":"Bring forth therefore fruits meet for repentance:","year":26}]}
